sequenceDiagram
  participant U as User
  participant FE as Frontend
  participant BE as Backend
  participant V as Vector DB
  participant O as Ollama

  U->>FE: Ask question
  FE->>BE: GET /api/v1/query?q=...
  BE->>V: similarity_search(k=5)
  V-->>BE: top-k chunks
  BE->>O: generate(prompt+context)
  O-->>BE: answer
  BE-->>FE: response JSON